structure.unit: ARTICLE VIII. FIFTH AND SIXTH CENT LOCAL OPTION GAS TAX

text.section:
Sec. 29-74. Statutory authority.
This article is adopted and shall be subject to the provisions of Section 336.025, 1984 Supplement of Florida Statutes, as amended by Section 33 of the 1985 Florida House and Senate Conference Committee Amendments to Committee Substitute for House Bill 1392.
